testsuite.name: com.loyalty.avenger.cashlock.specification.GetCashLockSpec

testcase.name: TC-1. When Active collector lock their redemption from mobile channel= (cash redemption = true )then the collector is not able to redeem points from their account .
TC-2. When Active collector unlock their redemption from mobile (cash redemption = false) then the collector is able to redeem points from their account .
TC-3. When Active collector lock their redemption from WEB (cash redemption = true) then collector is not able to redeem points from their account .
TC-4. When Active collector unlock their redemption from WEB (cash redemption = false) then collector is able to redeem points from their account .
TC-5. When Active collector lock their redemption from Celo Green (GRSC) (cash redemption = true) then collector is not able to redeem points from their account .
TC-6. When Active collector unlock their redemption from mobile (cash redemption = false) then collector is able to redeem points from their account .
TC-7. When dormant collector lock their redemption from WEB (cash redemption = true) then collector is not able to redeem points from their account .
TC-8. When dormant collector unlock their redemption from WEB (cash redemption = false) then collector is able to redeem points from their account .
TC-09. When Victim collector try to update their cash redemption from WEB the collector is not able to access their account and get Error 403 forbidden .
TC-10. When Closed collector try to update their cash redemption from WEB the collector is not able to access their account and get Error 403 forbidden .
TC-11. When Cancelled collector try to update their cash redemption from WEB the collector is not able to access their account and get Error 403 forbidden .
